---
title: Farmhouse Chicken Thighs with Brown Butter 'Champ' Mash
description: Wholesome farmhouse-style flavours come together in this satisfying supper, but the potatoes are the real champion on the plate. Toasty brown butter and zesty green onions add a touch of Irish-inspired charm to plain ol' mashed potatoes.
